<subSubSection pageId="252" pageNumber="530" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="252.[787,1381,1503,1930]" pageId="252" pageNumber="530">
<taxonomicName box="[788,1053,1666,1695]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Andalgalomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="252" pageNumber="530" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="olrogi">Andalgalomys olrogi</taxonomicName>
is the type species of the genus. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Mares &amp; Braun" authorityYear="1996" box="[947,1195,1700,1733]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Andalgalomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="252" pageNumber="530" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="roigi">Andalgalomys roigi</taxonomicName>
is subsumed under A. 
<taxonomicName box="[920,988,1748,1773]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Andalgalomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="252" pageNumber="530" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="olrogi">olrogi</taxonomicName>
, based on karyologycal, molecular, and morphological grounds. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
